onCompletion

java.lang.Object onCompletion(Event event,
                              EventStatus status)
                              throws java.lang.InterruptedException
Hands over an event request following completion of processing. Clients may use this call-back to report on event completion or provide their own annotations.

Returns:
An optional object that is stored as an annotation on the request
Throws:
java.lang.InterruptedException - Thrown if interrupted.
